  "page": "Illyrio Mopatis's first wife",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\"><img alt=\"Pentos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/50px-Pentos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/75px-Pentos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/100px-Pentos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Illyrio's first wife</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\"><img alt=\"Pentos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/50px-Pentos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/75px-Pentos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/100px-Pentos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Illyrio&#39;s first wife by Amuelia.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg/221px-Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg\" width=\"221\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg/331px-Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3c/Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg/441px-Illyrio%27s_first_wife_by_Amuelia.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Illyrio's first wife by Amuelia</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentoshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>first wife</b> of Magister <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> was a cousin of the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio_Mopatis%27s_first_wife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>With the aid of <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>, Illyrio Mopatis reached a position where the daughter of a Magister was willing to marry him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Illyrio upset the cousin of his first wife, the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a>, after he married <a href=\"/index.php/Serra\" title=\"Serra\">Serra</a>, a former bedslave he had bought and come to love. The Prince of Pentos closed the palace to Illyrio forever.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio_Mopatis%27s_first_wife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio_Mopatis%27s_first_wife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>As they travel through <a href=\"/index.php/Andalos\" title=\"Andalos\">Andalos</a>, Illyrio tells Tyrion of his first and second wives.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio_Mopatis%27s_first_wife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Month/2002/08/\">ConJosé (San JoséE, CA; Ausust 29-September 2) (Augustus 29, 2002)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_5\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 5\">Chapter 5</a>, Tyrion II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405023716\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.097 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.436 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 566/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10494/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5855/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 535/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1188/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7